textBeforeTable: Sizing in inches/centimeters: Chest/Girth: Measure girth around the broadest part of the chest and add 2". Neck: Measure the circumference of pet's neck for a snug fit. No need to add inches as you would with a collar. Back: Measure length of pet's back from the base of the neck to the base of the tail. See below for estimating by breed. Note: If the dog has a stout build, select one size larger. Imported Machine wash in cold water on gentle cycle. Line dry. Leg straps for a comfortable, secure fit 100% acrylic East Side Collection® Cozy Cable Knit Dog Sweaters have intricate cable patterns that add texture and warmth, ideal for fall and wintertime wear.
